```typescript
// Request
{ email: string; password: string; }

// Response: SingleResponse<{ user: User; jwt: string; }>
```

**`GET /v1/admin/auth/me`**

```typescript
// Response: SingleResponse<User>

interface User {
  id: string;
  email: string;
  name: string;
  avatar_url: string | null;
